snippet.title: Voltage High Society Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Voltage High Society on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2063480/Voltage_High_Society/

Enter. Evolve. Escape.

Voltage High Society is a cyberpunk-bodyhorror-metroidvania. You are a nameless prisoner thrown into an island ruled by cybernetic monsters. Fight your way through the horrors, gain new weapons and abilities, and look for a way out. Inspired by Japanese cyberpunk and Escape from New York, featuring gritty retro graphics with modern touches.
